Title: A Witness to History
Description:
I will gather up the other Tauren pilgrims and we will travel into the Vale together.

Meet me at the Gate of the August Celestials at the southern edge of Kun-Lai Summit and speak with me there.
ObjectivesText: Speak with Sunwalker Dezco at the Gate of the August Celestials.

Objectives.Text: Speak with Dezco at the Gate of the August Celestials
